    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2021-06-11</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2022-01-24T19:22:11Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>National Science and Technology Strategy Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Office of Science and Technology Policy (OSTP) to develop a national science and technology strategy and publish a science and technology review.</p> <p>The bill revises OSTP reporting requirements to direct the OSTP to submit to Congress a comprehensive national science and technology strategy of the United States to meet national research and development objectives for the following four-year period.</p> <p>No later than December 31, 2022, and every four years afterwards, the OSTP shall complete a review of the science and technology enterprise of the United States. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>07</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2022-02-18</actionDate>
